### Variables
# @baseUrl = http://localhost:1337
@baseUrl = https://motorhome-be.onrender.com
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api

### Get all trabalhos
GET {{apiUrl}}/trabalhos
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get trabalhos with population (include relations)
GET {{apiUrl}}/trabalhos?populate=*
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get single trabalho by ID
GET {{apiUrl}}/trabalhos/htr7lui2y2sepa7xoyigtlv1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get single trabalho with population
GET {{apiUrl}}/trabalhos/htr7lui2y2sepa7xoyigtlv1?populate=*
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Sorting example (descending by createdAt)
GET {{apiUrl}}/trabalhos?sort=createdAt:desc
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get trabalho by slug
GET {{apiUrl}}/trabalhos?filters[slug][$eq]=exemplo-de-trabalho
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Admin endpoints (require authentication)
### Login to admin (get JWT token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/auth/local
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Use JWT token for authenticated requests
# @name login
# Use the token from the login response above
@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### Get trabalhos with authentication
GET {{apiUrl}}/trabalhos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/_health
Content-Type: application/json

